snippet.title: Snops Attack! Zombie Defense (Xbox Indie Game) Hard Difficulty Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Snops Attack! Zombie Defense playthrough on Hard difficulty settings. This is my 3rd attempt at this game. 1st run barely made it with last life. 2nd run finished with 8 lives to spare. 3rd run lets get this thing recorded on hard difficulty.
